cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with video representation learning using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed framework involves unsupervised learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves video synthesis and rendering, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
